      "content": "Subject: Reminder of Punctuality Expectations\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has been consistently observed over the past two weeks - your daily tardiness to work. While we understand that unforeseen circumstances can occasionally cause delays, it has come to our attention that you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late each day.\n\nAs a dedicated member of our team, your punctuality is essential to maintaining the smooth operation of our workplace. We kindly ask that you make a concerted effort to arrive at your scheduled start time. Your timely arrival will demonstrate your commitment to your role and our company.\n\nThank you for your understanding and cooperation. Should there be any obstacles that prevent you from arriving on time, please inform your supervisor promptly so we can address any ongoing issues.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Your Contact Information]",
